    p Forgot your password? Submit a patch request with new password and passwordConfirm to #{url}.
    p (Website for this action is not implemented yet)
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
                td(align='left')
                    table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset Your Password
    p If you didn't ignore this password.Please ignore this email.
